Languages which produces Erlang VM bytecode:
 - Erlang
 - Efene http://efene.tumblr.com/
 - LFE http://github.com/rvirding/lfe

BEAM recompiler to JVM:
 - http://wiki.github.com/krestenkrab/erjang/ - very intersting.
   - http://www.javalimit.com/

Using Erlang style concurenncy in JS:
 - http://beatniksoftware.com/erjs/
 - http://www.neilmix.com/2007/02/07/threading-in-javascript-17/

There is also other systems, languages and libraries for some languages which are influenced by Erlang.


Alternative Erlang runtime and VM. Actually interpreter, not VM. By Maxim Kharchenko
  http://github.com/maximk/teeterl#readme
  http://taooferlang.blogspot.com/
